        tag: "ZONE 02 · RIVERS & WATER CANYONS", 
        h2: "White-Water Kayaking & River Snorkeling", 
        body: "Domptez rushing river rapids and drift between carved narrow stone canyons. Learn freshwater snorkeling in hidden crystal clear mountain rockpools.", 
